<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>이메일 인증</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #6d28d9;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .logo span {
      font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
    }
    .divider {
      width: 80px;
      height: 2px;
      background-color: #a78bfa;
      margin: 20px auto;
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0 10px;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .code-box {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: inline-block;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    .code-label {
      color: #6d28d9;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .code {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #6d28d9;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <span style="font-style: italic;">Cult</span><span>🖱ick</span>
    </div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="title">이메일 인증 번호 안내</div>
    <div class="message">
      안녕하세요. CultPick입니다.<br>
      아래 인증번호를 입력하여 이메일 인증을 완료해주세요.
    </div>
    <div class="code-box">
      <div class="code-label">확인 코드</div>
      <div class="code">{{code}}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
